						               													<description>The CEO Fukumoto has decided to give a bonus to just one employee. But, as he likes games, he's said that whoever can guess who that was, will share the bonus with that character.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Out of 20 roles, one is put out of the game, and the goal of the game is for the remaining players to guess what role that is. The remaining 19 roles will be dealt to the players, and the players will use these as &amp;quot;connections&amp;quot; in the company to find out what other cards the other players have. Your cards will be revealed by the actions of other players, but once face up, they will have additional effects that work to your advantage.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first player to figure out the card that was put away, is the winner of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Arclight Twenty is a game of deduction.  It&amp;rsquo;s a memorabilia for 20 years anniversary of Arclight Inc., and was given only to the people that have involved in their jobs.  It is said only 400 copies are printed.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
